    "texte_orig": "I[SP]don't[SP]care[SP]what[SP]happens[SP]anymore![SP]I'm[SP]just\ngoing[SP]to[SP]stay[SP]here[SP]and[SP]listen[SP]to[SP]the[SP]song.\nI'll[SP]be[SP]here[SP]even[SP]if[SP]I[SP]die!",
