    "texte_orig": "I[SP]wonder[SP]if[SP]crises[SP]stimulate[SP]man's[SP]brain...[1205][U+000F]\nNew[SP]songs[SP]are[SP]leaping[SP]from[SP]me,[SP]one[SP]after\nanother.",
